  <cite><strong><a href="http://danielcollectiveidea.com">Daniel Morrison</a></strong> </cite> said 8 days later:<br />
  <p>Hey Kevin,</p>


	<p>I thought you were pretty spot-on with the original article.  I came back today so I could forward the URL to some folks.  Thanks for writing these up.</p>


	<p>Pagination, as a concept is often just annoying.  I find that I take it out of production apps more than I add it in.</p>


	<p>IMHO, those of us that have a number of production sites realize that a lot of the cool Rails bits really just get in the way.</p>
